OL,3,CNo covert recording devices found in
OL,4,Cpolice searches of Holyrood toilets
OL,6,FPolice Scotland has carried out checks
OL,7,Fof the Scottish Parliament in the wake
OL,8,Fof allegations that a hidden camera
OL,9,Fwas placed inside toilets in the
OL,10,Fbuilding.
OL,12,FIt is understood MSP Colin Smyth, who
OL,13,Fhas been arrested and charged in
OL,14,Fconnection with possession of indecent
OL,15,Fimages, also faces a further charge in
OL,16,Frelation to the allegations.
OL,18,FScottish Parliament bosses confirmed
OL,19,Fon Thursday night that the South
OL,20,FScotland MSP has had his Holyrood pass
OL,21,F"deactivated".
