OL,3,CNo covert recording devices found in
OL,4,Cpolice searches of Holyrood toilets
OL,6,FThere will also be "enhanced
OL,7,Fadditional checks" going forward,
OL,8,Fthose working at the parliament have
OL,9,Fbeen told.
OL,11,FIn a letter sent to all building users
OL,12,Fon Friday, Presiding Officer Alison
OL,13,FJohnstone and Scottish Parliament
OL,14,Fchief executive David McGill said
OL,15,Fsearches have been carried out and "no
OL,16,Fcovert recording devices have been
OL,17,Ffound".
