OL,3,CNo covert recording devices found in
OL,4,Cpolice searches of Holyrood toilets
OL,6,FThey acknowledged "deeply concerning
OL,7,Freports" of the story in the media
OL,8,Fwould cause "unease and anxiety" for
OL,9,Fthose working in the Holyrood building.
OL,11,FThe letter said: "We can confirm that
OL,12,FPolice Scotland, with our support,
OL,13,Fhave conducted a full sweep of all
OL,14,Ftoilets and changing rooms in our
OL,15,Fbuilding and that no covert recording
OL,16,Fdevices have been found.
OL,18,F"We have also instructed that enhanced
OL,19,Fadditional checks to our existing
OL,20,Fsecurity sweeps of the building take
OL,21,Fplace going forward."
