OL,3,CNo covert recording devices found in
OL,4,Cpolice searches of Holyrood toilets
OL,6,FMs Johnstone and Mr McGill sought to
OL,7,Freassure staff that their safety and
OL,8,Fwelfare is a "priority", as they said
OL,9,Fpeople should be "confident to use the
OL,10,Fbuilding as you would normally".
OL,12,FSmyth was arrested on 5 August and is
OL,13,Fdue to appear in court at a later date.
OL,15,FHe was first elected as an MSP in 2016
OL,16,Fand returned to Holyrood again at the
OL,17,F2021 election.
