OL,6,FThe Scottish Parliament website now
OL,7,Flists him as an independent, with
OL,8,FLabour confirming he had had the whip
OL,9,Fremoved pending the investigation.
OL,11,FIn a statement at the time, the MSP
OL,12,Fsaid: "These events have come as a
OL,13,Fshock and this is a deeply stressful
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,F"I am obviously co-operating fully
OL,17,Fwith any inquiries and hope the matter
OL,18,Fcan be resolved quickly.
